-- Rwanda Genocide Suspect Pastor Uwinkindi Pleads Not Guilty at Tribunal
-- Sarah McGregor
-- 2010-07-09T12:10:35Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-09/rwanda-genocide-suspect-pastor-uwinkindi-pleads-not-guilty-at-tribunal.html

          
          
             Jean-Bosco Uwinkindi, a 59-year-old
former Rwandan pastor, pleaded not guilty to charges including
genocide at his first appearance at the International Criminal
Tribunal for Rwanda, the United Nations-backed court said.  
 Uwinkindi also faces charges of conspiracy to commit
genocide and extermination as a crime against humanity, the
Arusha, Tanzania-based tribunal said in an e-mailed statement
today.  
